Removed french, spanish and german FMV.

Chicken Run for Dreamcast takes players through 20 huge levels of Tweedy Farm as they lead Ginger and her friends to freedom. With a nest filled of gameplay, players need tojump over obstacles, sneak through the pie machine, and avoid Mrs. Tweedy's attack dogs! Chicken Run features artwork and game levels based on the movie; roosters and hens of all ages can take part in this feathered adventure over and over again.
* All of your favorite characters from the movie including Ginger, Rocky, Babs, Mac, and Fowler.
* Four unique environments based on actual movie stills including the Farmyard Area and Mrs. Tweedy's pie machine.
* Actual images from the movie to help advance the story.
* Password system to save progress.
* Combination of platform and puzzle solving gameplay